Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,離開了馬克蘭之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:15.89,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,註：馬克蘭，意為“森林之地”，維京人抵達北美的據點之一，推測位於加拿大拉布拉多地區。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們的船進一步往南航行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,海風告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前方有更豐饒的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然後我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,新大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:49.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,碩果纍纍 綠草茵茵的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我給這片土地取了個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.49,Vinland-pronunciation,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,1000)}    Vinland
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,名叫「文蘭」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.71,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,註：文蘭，意為“草原之地”，維京人抵達北美的據點之一，\N現有考古遺蹟證明在加拿大紐芬蘭島北端一帶。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,對本大爺雷夫·埃里克森有點改觀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.67,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,註：據史詩記載，他是第一位發現美洲的歐洲探險家，比哥倫布早500年。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.98,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好厲害 雷夫大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:16.94,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然後呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:17.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那裡有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那裡暖和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,比冰島還要大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,對啊 比這裡暖和多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.83,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,草原一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們還遇到了原住民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.61,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雖然語言不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是沒多久我們就成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:43.52,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這些羽飾和這根煙杆就是他們送的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,聽好了 這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.88,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有真正的戰士才能佩戴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:55.18,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,你看 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.96,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 原來孩子們還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.77,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,大叔讓我摸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:07.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我想給他們聽一聽雷夫先生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真正的戰士啊 大叔果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我說的沒錯吧 托爾芬真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,等你長大後就來坐我的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,現在就讓我坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是很奇怪啊 雷夫大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因為我爺爺說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-pronunciation,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,1000)}                Jörmungandr
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大海的西邊有耶夢加得 會把靠近的船都吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,註：北歐神話中環繞人世的巨大海蛇，被奧丁扔進了無底深海之中。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然後再往西就什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:38.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所以說啊 正是因為這樣才襯托出我的偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.82,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你看 這個就是證據 證明我是真正的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可是雷夫大叔你本來就不是戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.79,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你真是沒搞明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是只有打仗的才叫做戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:53.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,水手要和大海戰鬥 這可不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.12,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大家都在說 大叔是長了鬍子的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,就知道冒險 打仗的事情上一點都幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你們只會人云亦云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾芬應該相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你覺得不去打仗只會冒險的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所說的話都不可信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:25.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因為如果是說我爸爸是戰士 那倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.98,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這些小鬼竟然瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你給我狠狠地說教下他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好了 今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,亞雷 送他們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好的 托爾茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:45.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,格陵蘭那裡有人凍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,今年的寒流也會更強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大部分家畜應該都會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:16.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但真正的問題是氣候正在逐年變冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.36,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有這兩隻變虛弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,很冷吧 尤爾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,讓叔叔給你暖一下身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,色老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,媽媽 快睡吧 不然又要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,沒事的 來幫我牽一下羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看來這裡的情況也不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,說不定哪年冬天會冷到沒人能熬過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:57.25,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在我的國家那邊 我的弟弟正在計劃遷居
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,得遷很遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我可是往返一週回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,文蘭就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾芬船長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,耶夢加得出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,放馬過來吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐 去自己的床上睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.74,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,兩個人太擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:43.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真狡猾 這張床是我先暖好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.79,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他們還在聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:55.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不用管他們 解決煩心事是大人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,別看他們了 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐給你抱一抱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們家不買奴隸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.61,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,媽媽身體又不好 得要我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,別人家是別人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要每年都問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤爾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.74,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,還以為要摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:38.87,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,沒受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這下面…有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤爾瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,吶 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,昨天的故事有多少是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:20.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,全都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 讓我坐坐這艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我親眼見到的話就相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:28.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你這話的意思就是不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這麼想坐船的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,坐你爸的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看 那裡還有艘軍船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好像是村子裡代代相傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸會很樂意借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親是個小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.81,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,拜託幾次了都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾芬 這附近的海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我在年輕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,被浮冰困住過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因為那時才移居到格陵蘭不久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所以大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,食物很快就吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只能靠吃冰來充飢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,最後船被冰川碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:19.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們走投無路 只能在海上行走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,等我回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,就只剩下我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,其他六個伙伴都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們付出這麼大代價
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,也要在這北方的島上居住下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,赫爾加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,快煮熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤爾瓦 拿獸皮來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.39,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這人埋在雪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看著就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這怎麼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,讓火燒旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,吶 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他已經死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,手腳都爛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,而且這個人有點麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是這個村的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.97,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.94,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會在暴風雪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,還問為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他是逃走的奴隸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,要是把他藏在這 會引發糾紛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們是逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:47.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們的先祖以前居住在更東的土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.26,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那片土地名叫挪威
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,比這裡更溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,海也不會結冰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.82,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,有諸多海灣環繞的一塊好土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.37,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,一個名為哈拉爾的強大男人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈拉爾的軍隊以燎原之勢 鎮壓了各個村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,註：哈拉爾一世（約850-933年），綽號“金髮”哈拉爾，第一位挪威國王。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他自詡為首次統一全挪威的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,成為了挪威的統治者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然後他逼迫所有人做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:23.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,服從國王 或者離開挪威這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,許多人厭惡哈拉爾的惡政
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,移居到了其統治範圍之外的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:35.18,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那就是這裡 冰島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.97,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大叔果然是騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親和我的祖先們怎麼會逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,冒險老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.10,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雷夫大叔說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.55,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,別處的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,逃來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,活…活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你 能說名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.46,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,火 尤爾瓦 再燒旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:48.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我會被帶回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,回到哈夫丹大人的宅邸裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:52.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,果然是從山的另一邊過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.88,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我不要回去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:03.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:09.73,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我能去哪裡…沒有目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹到港口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那幫人又來找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有你能應付得來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那幫人說著什麼奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,強行上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雖然有雷夫先生在中間調解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但年輕人都按捺不住想去幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,反正快來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是唯一適合人類的頸飾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,既不是金也不是銀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是鐵做的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:53.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有把鎖鏈繫在脖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:56.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,人類才有點利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.44,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不該這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我有一隻奴隸掙斷鎖鏈逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.25,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你們有見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,別找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,反正就是為之前的事而來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.31,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,三番五次的 真是一群懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,和他們已經爭執了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.65,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,以為聚多點人我就會怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.80,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前些天剛在居民大會上調停過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那次打架 我被你砍掉了左手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我也記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,竟然敢砍掉我大哥的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.44,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,住手 亞雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大哥已經不能再走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我要把這混蛋的腿也給砍掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,法律和居民大會都吃屎去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈…哈夫丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,給你繫上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,輕視法律者不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,法律即為鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,心術不正的傢伙要被繫上鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.89,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,才能開始成為一名人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,逃走的是個年輕的斯拉夫男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.18,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你們有見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:46.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我第一次體驗到這麼安穩的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,清醒過來 不然會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.63,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大家都在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.80,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因為大家都被賣到了不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:26.10,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在遙遠的西方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:28.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在海的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:31.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,有一塊叫做「文蘭」 的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:37.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那裡氣候溫暖 物產豐盛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,奴隸商人和戰火也無法到達的遠方土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:44.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.09,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,將來與我們一起到那片土地去生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:54.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,文蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:22:59.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這裡叫文蘭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:20.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:22.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,原諒我的無禮 托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:26.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我是那個奴隸正當的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父…父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,來這邊 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:34.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是藏起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.85,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你的奴隸快要死了 我們是在救他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:44.66,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,這個男人 多少錢買的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:51.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父…父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:54.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,問那種事情很不禮貌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:56.36,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,兩頭羊 年輕的母羊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.71,0:23:57.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我給你三頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:58.85,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:02.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎樣 哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我要帶那傢伙回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,必須在其他奴隸面前拷打他 以儆效尤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.46,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那就四頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:20.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 聽不懂哈夫丹大人說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:22.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:25.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,如果我說加倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.41,0:24:28.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:30.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,全部都是三歲以下的母羊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:40.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,八頭羊換個快死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:45.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是一單好買賣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.97,0:24:51.32,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,騙人吧 成交了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:56.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.45,0:24:59.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你以為這就能解開那傢伙的鎖鏈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:02.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然後你能把他帶到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.51,0:25:10.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,羊就讓我們來挑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.64,0:25:27.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐 很傷心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:29.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,肯定傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.19,0:25:30.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,用八頭羊換的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.87,0:25:32.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,馬上就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:36.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.57,0:25:38.92,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怪傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:39.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:43.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們也是逃過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:45.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雷夫大叔說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.59,0:25:49.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我們的祖先是從東方逃過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.16,0:25:53.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,說是逃來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 據說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.00,0:26:04.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.54,0:26:14.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那麼想從這裡逃走的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.75,0:26:18.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,又能逃到哪裡呢
